## .DS_Store and similar files are automatically excluded by R CMD build
## ========================================
## GitHub files
## ========================================
^\.github/

## .Rdata and .Rhistory are automatically excluded by R CMD build
## ========================================
## R/RStudio files
## ========================================
^.*\.Rproj$
^\.Rproj\.user$


## ========================================
## Package development
## ========================================
^_pkgdown\.yml$
^data-raw/

## ========================================
## Build outputs
## ========================================
## We could exclude NEWS.md, README.md, LICENSE.md etc.
## But good to have those files in tar.gz... 
## We could doc as well, but this provides offline vignette
^README\.Rmd$ # exclude Rmd file keep md file
^docs/ # Website (built by pkgdown)
^Meta/  # Offline vignette data (built by devtools) 

## ========================================
## Personal helper scripts
## ========================================
^(M|m)akefile$
^_create_.*
^_update_.*
^_call_.*

^doc$
^Meta$
